@NODE E5 "hISTORY"

@{fg fill}The history...@{fg text}

V2.0 (09-Mar-97):
-----------------

  o  Included a MUI preference program for configuration.

  o  Fixed a bug that caused a wait after the last shown entry in
     the nonstop mode.

  o  Fixed some ugly bugs which caused Zippy not to start.

  o  Fixed some stacksize problems.

  o  Improved code.

  o  Included installer script for easy installation.

  o  Included 68000/020/030/040/060 versions.



V1.3 (06-Mar-96):
-----------------
  o  Internal dECiSiON release.



V1.2 (28-Sep-96):
-----------------

  o  Zippy runs much more stable since great FAME improvements.

  o  Additional minor code improvements.

  o  Some garbage removed.

  o  Scan buffer is now 1 meg maximum, because the first
     buffer has to be filled before the search is launched.



V1.1 (05-May-96):
-----------------

  o  Minor code improvements.

@ENDNODE

